sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Underwriter as Human Underwriter / Queue
    participant Ingestion as FastAPI Ingestion
    participant Orchestrator as LangGraph Orchestrator
    participant Worker as Specialist Agents (Data/Income/Credit/Risk)
    participant Policy as Policy & Compliance Agent (RAG)
    participant Critic as Adjudication Critic
    participant Writer as Explanation Writer Agent
    participant HumanEsc as Human Escalation Agent
    participant DB as SQLite / Chroma Vector DB
    participant ML as LightGBM Risk Model (SHAP)

    Underwriter->>Ingestion: Submit Loan Application (SK_ID_CURR)
    Ingestion->>Orchestrator: Initialize State Machine
    Orchestrator->>Worker: Dispatch Data Assembly
    Worker->>DB: Query 7 tables (Bureau, Application, etc.)
    DB-->>Worker: Return Raw Tables
    Worker-->>Orchestrator: Return ApplicantFile (typed)

    Orchestrator->>Worker: Verify Income & Credit History (Parallel)
    Worker-->>Orchestrator: Verified Income + Credit Summary (Thin-File flag)

    alt Thin File Flagged
        Orchestrator->>HumanEsc: Route to Human Escalation
        HumanEsc->>DB: Write ReferralPackage
        HumanEsc-->>Underwriter: Notify Referral Queue
    else Standard File
        Orchestrator->>Worker: Risk Scoring
        Worker->>ML: Pass Feature Vector
        ML-->>Worker: Calibrated PD + SHAP Factors
        Worker-->>Orchestrator: Return RiskScoringResult

        Orchestrator->>Policy: Policy Verification & Fairness Auditing
        Policy->>DB: Query policy embeddings (Chroma)
        DB-->>Policy: Return Top-K Policy Clauses (Hit/Miss)
        Policy-->>Orchestrator: Return Compliance & Fairness Results

        Orchestrator->>Critic: Submit Draft Decision Package
        Critic->>Critic: Verify Faithfulness (SHAP vs Text) & Guardrails
        
        alt Critique Fails (Revision loop, max 1 retry)
            Critic->>Orchestrator: Request Re-run / Refinement
            Orchestrator->>Worker: Refine outputs
            Worker-->>Orchestrator: Return Refined outputs
            Orchestrator->>Critic: Re-submit Package
        end

        alt Approved by Critic
            Orchestrator->>Writer: Generate Grounded Explanation
            Writer->>DB: Fetch Regulator Adverse-Action Codes
            DB-->>Writer: Return Citation Texts
            Writer->>Writer: Compile Narrative with Citations
            Writer-->>Orchestrator: Return DecisionRecord
            Orchestrator->>Underwriter: Publish Recommendation to Queue
        else Rejected or Low Confidence
            Orchestrator->>HumanEsc: Route to Human Escalation
            HumanEsc->>DB: Compile referral package
            HumanEsc-->>Underwriter: Notify Referral Queue
        end
    end
